<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.4.2">
<l>vaṅka maṟikaṭal vaṇṇā māmuki lēyok kunampī</l>
<l>ceṅka ṇeṭiya tiruvē ceṅkama lampurai vāyā</l>
<l>koṅkai curantiṭa vuṉṉai kūviyuṅ kāṇā tiruntēṉ</l>
<l>eṅki runtāyarka ḷōṭu meṉviḷai yāṭu kiṉṟāyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You the hue of the sea where waves swell, prince who resembles dark clouds,</l>
<l>Tall bright-eyed treasure, oh, mouth like a red lotus,</l>
<l>As my breasts truly overflowed, though I called you, without seeing [you],</l>
<l rend="indent">I waited.</l>
<l>Where and what are you [still] playing with the herders?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
